description: Application for the approval of reserved matters (siting design, external appearance of buildings and landscaping, and renewable energy (Condition 32) of the residential and open space parts of the site only to facilitate the erection of 126 residential units and a park) attached as a condition to planning permission ref 06/P0984 (dated 28/07/2009) relating to redevelopment providing a mixed used scheme comprising 1.74 hectares of residential development (Use Class C3) and community uses (Use Class D1) up to 600 sq.m; 1.78 hectares of employment use (Use Class B1) up to 7,500 sq.m and public open space 0.45 hectares.
